{"data":[{"id":561746835,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","url_token":"lian-ke-30","name":"假语","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7f20c63f898cb67cf0620d862011fc7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e0ce809ba0adc98e09e7cd55dcdf9901","user_type":"people","headline":"十分冷淡存知己，一曲微茫度此生。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":296,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561746835","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545995761,"updated_time":1546003532,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":128,"comment_count":45,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲失败了，是哗众取宠的小丑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个人群嘲成功了，那就是睥睨四顾的成功人士了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你看，刚刚骂人家骂得正爽，觉得这种脑子的人这辈子都不能成功，可是一转眼，他现在就已经从一个民科升华成了一个移动的流量大v了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然他现在看起来还是个民科也或者高一新生。但是你看看别人关注数量，很多人拿赞同数量举例。其实他们根本不明白赞同和关注的区别\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d25c224c83666220bfb82aca032c6b88_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4300b94a46bfa6ca4a7fdd04f0e76c28_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e再看看别人的回答流量，虽然不知道他本意是否是炒作。但是这19k的关注。和浑身上下自带的流量，加上知乎这个平台对于高关注用户的偏爱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且，19k的关注远远不是终点，现在热度还没有停止呢，并且知乎也在为了热度恶意的引导着流量\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人不相信我，那我便举几个例子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-189dfb2f18f13a950983e375a04f6735_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-873718197d230676a4bd114a04b858ef_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e比如这位叶青大v，他积攒了几年的粉丝为18k。用了几年的时间，而最开始他还仅仅只是一个不知名用户的时候，就依靠阅读流量获得了极多邀请合作，以及在答案里面植入广告的邀请。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而我们的高中生，证明大v。却坐拥19k的活跃用户关注，其中还包括不少大v。也就是他最少也足以在短期内达到叶青大v层次的水平，一些说只值几百块钱的朋友，我只能说你对于流量变现太没有概念了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-332a112e8701690a2baa07e90efa66ea_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4a105753bf6a5a3a0b6357c059e54ca5_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='1480'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1480\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-55ac1a6ce35f310e36bb2b29f0b34ce0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b681d3de365f887656932acf0ebb33d7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e而这个问题的流量更是可怕至极，如图所示。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前来说他的帐号价值已经上了六位数以上了。这是什么意思。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也就是人家选择最愚蠢的变现方式，把这个账号卖了。也足以变现数十万了，至于其他的各种变现方式，最简单就是成为一个大v开一个公众号。流量变现。足以让他在高中就月入五位数，如果经营得好。足以让自己年收入比得上一个小资家庭的年收入了，高考加分也无非请人代笔发表一篇简简单单的论文再背上一背。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在这个帐号那怕是拿来给我这种不怎么熟悉知乎各种潜规则的人来运用，也足以达成月入过万这种小目标，而给某些人能够产生的流量更是难以直接计算。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想想人家高一就能赚数十万，想出如此的完美炒作方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕是哗众取宠。人家也已经成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个案例足以位列知乎最近三年成功的钓鱼案例。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们对于钓鱼者的冷嘲热讽也无非是在赠送流量，为他的变现添砖加瓦。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也不知道是有预谋的炒作还是天意如此。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只知道，他确实成功了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个成功者，还是值得我献上一点敬意的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那怕，靠的只是运气\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"一个人群嘲失败了，是哗众取宠的小丑。一个人群嘲成功了，那就是睥睨四顾的成功人士了。你看，刚刚骂人家骂得正爽，觉得这种脑子的人这辈子都不能成功，可是一转眼，他现在就已经从一个民科升华成了一个移动的流量大v了虽然他现在看起来还是个民科也或者高…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cu